          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-bottom: 60px;">
          <div style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
            <h3 style="color: #00B45A; font-size: 21px;">Please confirm your email</h3>
          </div>
          <p style="font-size: 15px; opacity: 0.6; color: #223354; margin-bottom: 25px;">Thank you for signing up!</p>
          <p style="font-size: 15px; opacity: 0.6; color: #223354; margin-bottom: 25px;">Please click on the button below to get started.</p>
          <div style="margin-bottom: 40px;">
            <a href=`{{url}}/auth/accept/{{token}}` style="text-decoration: none; background-color: #00B45A; color: #fff; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15px; display: inline-block; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5;">Confirm your email</a>
          </div>
          <p style="font-size: 15px; opacity: 0.6; color: #223354; margin-bottom: 25px;">If you didnâ€™t sign up for this, you can ignore this email or contact support if you have questions.</p>
          <div style="margin: 50px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(34, 51, 84, 0.2); padding-bottom: 33px;">
            <p style="font-size: 15px; opacity: 0.6; color: #223354; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-top: 0;">Welcome & Thanks!</p>
            <p style="font-size: 15px; opacity: 0.6; color: #223354; margin-bottom: 25px; opacity: 1; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-top: 0;">PMS Team</p>
          </div>
       </div>
      </div>
      <div style="background: rgba(182, 182, 182, 0.2); text-align: center; padding: 65px 0;">
        <p style="font-size: 15px; color: #223354; margin-bottom: 6px;">{{year}} PMS</p>
 
      </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
